 auxiliá-lo a alcançar seus objetivos de forma eficaz e inovadora.</p>\n<p>Visão. Gerar em nossos clientes e na comunidade jurídica confiança e credibilidade em nosso trabalho.</p>\n<p>Valores. Ética, responsabilidade, profissionalismo, comprometimento com a causa e com o cliente.</p>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1865426 kc_col-sm-6 kc_column kc_col-sm-6\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1695660 kc_text_block\"></p>\n</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3410131 kc_row\"><div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\"><div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1768625 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column kc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"kc-col-container\"><div class=\"\"><h2 class=\"title-section\">Áreas de atuação</h2></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-462279 kc_row kc_row_inner\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1080161 kc_col-sm-3 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-3\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2584479 kc-icon-wrapper\">\n		<i class=\"fa-group\"></i>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-784727 kc_text_block\"><h3 class=\"h3\" style=\"text-align: center;\">FAMILIAR</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.</p>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-906291 kc_col-sm-3 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-3\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1278795 kc-icon-wrapper\">\n		<i class=\"fa-briefcase\"></i>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2016255 kc_text_block\"><h3 class=\"h3\" style=\"text-align: center;\">EMPRESARIAL</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium.</p>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1567343 kc_col-sm-3 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-3\"><div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"><div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3